voice_to_text: Why has Sarah Jessica Parker, even after seeing her husband cheat with her own eyes, refused to divorce him? In 1991, Sarah met Matthew Broderick and they came together because of their shared love for theater. After dating for six years, they officially got married. After marriage, the couple was very loving and welcome three children. They often attended events together and performed on Broadway. However, their marriage was not without challenges, as their relationship faced difficulties shortly after they got married. The gradually dull life after marriage made Matthew feel bored, so he secretly found several lovers. Reporters frequently caught Matthew on dates with his lover, even kissing them in bars. What's worse, he even brought his lover home for the night while Sarah was away. However, even after seeing these photos with her own eyes, Sarah refused to believe her husband had cheated. She said that unless her husband kissed another woman in front of her, she wouldn't believe the media's attempts to stir trouble. Matthew always maintained the image of a good man in front of her and the kids, which made it even harder for Sarah to leave him. Even if the whole world opposed their love, Sarah still loved Matthew. Now they have been married for almost 30 years. No matter what, we all hope Matthew will never betray Sarah again.

video_description: Cynthia Erivo ruined her hairline for just $1 million. #celebrity #fyb #CynthiaErivo
voice_to_text: Cynthia Erivo ruined her hairline for just one million dollar film salary. Her co star Ariana Grande just twirled around in a princess dress and pocketed $15 million. This British actress once had beautiful long hair. However, in 2,017, she suddenly cut it very short and dyed it blonde. Many speculated whether she had cancer and was undergoing chemotherapy because she appeared thin with sunken eyes at the time. In reality, Cynthia Erivo simply wanted to showcase her striking facial features. Later, for her role as Elphaba in Wicked, Cynthia shaved her head completely before filming. Her entire body had to be painted green and makeup artists used airbrushes to apply the makeup. They then contoured her face, a process that took at least four hours. She also had to wear fake ears, but this sometimes caused issues with her wig and exposed her hairline. To maintain the perfection of her look, she decisively shaved her head. Many people feel it's unfair for the 37 year old Cynthia Erivo. Wicked had a 150 million dollar budget, yet she was paid only one million dollars. Meanwhile, Ariana Grande, also a lead, was paid 15 times her salary. But Cynthia Arrivo never complains. She values the experience of acting over money. Whether it's waking up at 6 a m. For a run or tirelessly performing wire stunts, she embraces it all wholeheartedly.

voice_to_text: In May 2025, social media platforms buzzed with alarming rumours the infamous Haunted Annabelle doll had vanished during the Devils on the run paranormal tour. Reports claimed sightings in Texas, Chicago, and even linked her absence to a fire at Louisiana's historic Notoway resort. Speculation intensified when the doll was reportedly absent from a scheduled showing in Louisiana during the tour. However, the New England Society for Psychic Research, N E S P R, swiftly addressed these concerns. Dan Rivera, a lead investigator, shared a TikTok video confirming that Annabelle remains securely housed in her protective glass case the Warren's Occult Museum in Monroe, Connecticut. He stated, Annabelle is not missing. She's not in Chicago. This isn't the first time Annabelle's whereabouts have sparked public hysteria. In 2020, similar rumors circulated, prompting Tony Spara, the museum's director and son in law of Ed and Lorraine Warren, to reassure the public that the doll had never left the museum. Despite the museum's closure to the public in 2,019 due to zoning issues, Annabelle continues to captivate the public's imagination. She is scheduled to appear at the 2025 Rock Island Roadhouse Esoteric Expo in Illinois on October 4th.
